snippet.title: TetherGeist – Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: TetherGeist is a challenging yet satisfying pixel platformer. Using various unique movement mechanics, travel a mystical world to prove to the elders of your village... and to yourself... that you too can make the coming-of-age pilgrimage of your ancestors.
